				AdvanceLevel("Mining", 14);[/code]
Explaining the code:
[code]if (Mining < getLevelForXP(playerXP[14])) {
[/code] Commands the server to get XP required for a player to advance in the skill.
[code]playerLevel[14] = getLevelForXP(playerXP[14]);[/code] this shows that the player has indeed enough XP to advance in the level
[code]AdvanceLevel("Mining", 14);[/code]
Then finally, the player advances a level in this certain skill.

